"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-04-09-Olympic-rings-to-be-displayed-on-Eiffel-Tower-for-Paris-Games-1sFa2IGD26s-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN  Copied  Construction of the grandstands begins on the site of the Eiffel Tower Stadium, which will host the beach volleyball competitions during the upcoming Paris 2024 Olympics in Paris, France, April 6, 2024.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 392, \"end\": 397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998374278, \"rank\": 1.6262740488180543e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 399, \"end\": 405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9993210145868162, \"rank\": 0.00036170031011769027, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  The Olympic rings for the Paris Games will be displayed on the Eiffel Tower, the president of the monument's operating company (SETE) said.\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 567, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jean-Francois Martins said work to set the rings on the tower would begin at the end of the month after the Olympic torch has left ancient Olympia in Greece.\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 726, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 708, \"end\": 715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"score\": 0.9999081561276284, \"rank\": 9.185230847776811e-05, \"text\": \"Olympia\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\"}, {\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9992180105870226, \"rank\": 0.0007336173035417053, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The rings will be on the Seine side of the tower.\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999998385647, \"rank\": 1.614569213897284e-10, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Eiffel Tower will be a central part of the Paris Olympics, marking the 38-kilometer point of the marathon, while the beach volleyball event will be held at its base.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 947, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic flame will be positioned at the Jardin des Tuileries, near the Louvre.\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 1031, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 953, \"end\": 966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5647240870398919e-16, \"text\": \"Olympic flame\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games run from July 26 to August 11.\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinf